{"tid":2409763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲稱「送信給拜登」 老婦帶槍闖白宮遭特勤人員逮捕","createTime":"2021-02-16T05:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T05:58:10.000Z","uid":189046,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d542e2806f4a4b9849a1124cf0635a332ba68dc","tid":2409763,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210215/YP6B3USOSJEYZKSV5IWQ2TPPPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FYP6B3USOSJEYZKSV5IWQ2TPPPQ%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=2852fdba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FYP6B3USOSJEYZKSV5IWQ2TPPPQ%2F&h=c9d60504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210215/YP6B3USOSJEYZKSV5IWQ2TPPPQ/</a><br />\n美國特勤局(US Secret Service)證實，上周六(13日)下午，在白宮附近逮捕了一名聲稱要「送信給拜登」的老婦人與她的男伴，2人遭控無照持有槍枝、擁有未註冊槍枝與擁有未註冊但要等罪。<br />\n<br />\n《福斯新聞》報導，當天下午約5時40分，66歲女子霍爾(Sylvia Hall)與一名身分不明的男子，到白宮外的特勤檢查哨，向特勤人員表示，她有一封給拜登(Joe Biden)的信，要和拜登見個面。<br />\n<br />\n特勤人員隨即在男子身上搜出一把BB槍，立刻將他逮捕，接著搜索或爾的車，在車上發現一把並未登記且裝滿子彈的手槍，霍爾也遭到逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n特勤局表示，他們相信，當時並未對總統拜登，或任何由特勤局保護的人造成立即的威脅。被逮2人的動機仍待調查。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5444bbe7a31f45c3cc33a74e70b536db0a8d82","tid":2409763,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"465c04ea1a42d0f22572870188290f65a5f1c894","tid":2409763,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:27:54.000Z","msg":"彈劾失敗之後發生，咁岩嘅"},{"pid":"fcd28cfe714b661598bbaaa190c806b5161e5399","tid":2409763,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"特勤人員隨即在男子身上搜出一把BB槍，立刻將他逮捕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e2d3ebcd97e99e42f51828701580f8da290da4","tid":2409763,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"20年魔咒真係準"},{"pid":"decd263649113a68bfd262ee138f148de88fb0dd","tid":2409763,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"勇武"},{"pid":"97e15543c86bd4729666e5316a73894866ed73fb","tid":2409763,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dbc9cac56a0fd8ca417aef317cc3b758723563","tid":2409763,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcd28cfe714b661598bbaaa190c806b5161e5399","tid":2409763,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"特勤人員隨即在男子身上搜出一把BB槍，立刻將他逮捕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:58:10.000Z","msg":"好有香港黑警嘅影子"}]}